import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import "./index.css";
import Card from './Cards'

ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <Card
      imgsrc="https://picsum.photos/200"
      title="1st Netflix Original"
      sname="One hundred"
      link="https://youtube.com"
    />
    <Card
      imgsrc="https://picsum.photos/200"
      title="2nd Netflix Original"
      sname="Two hundred"
      link="https://youtube.com"
    />
    <Card
      imgsrc="https://picsum.photos/200"
      title="3rd Netflix Original"
      sname="Three hundred"
      link="https://youtube.com"
    />
  </>,
  document.getElementById("root")
);
